sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Pipeline Component<br/>(KFP SDK / TFX)
    participant UI as Pipeline UI /<br/>SDK Client
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as Database<br/>(MySQL 3306 / PostgreSQL 5432)

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType(name, properties)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE execution_type<br/>MySQL/PG protocol | Optional SSL | Username/password
    DB-->>MLMD: Type ID
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionTypeResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecution(execution, artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>Atomic operation
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>INSERT execution, artifacts, events, attributions
    DB-->>MLMD: Commit OK
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionResponse(execution_id, artifact_ids)

    KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts(artifacts)<br/>Record output artifacts (models, datasets, metrics)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact IDs
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutArtifactsResponse

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(starting_nodes, max_hops)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with recursive lineage traversal<br/>MySQL/PG protocol | Optional SSL | Username/password
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage graph rows
    MLMD-->>UI: LineageSubgraph(artifacts, executions,<br/>contexts, events, attributions, associations)

    UI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext(context_id)<br/>Query all artifacts in a pipeline run
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts JOIN attributions
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact records
    MLMD-->>UI: GetArtifactsByContextResponse

    Note over KFP,DB: Schema Migration (Startup)

    Note right of MLMD: --enable_database_upgrade=true
    MLMD->>DB: Check current schema version
    DB-->>MLMD: Current version
    MLMD->>DB: Execute migration_schemes[v].upgrade_queries
    DB-->>MLMD: Migration complete
    MLMD->>DB: Verify via verification_queries
    DB-->>MLMD: Schema verified
